indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Step 2. <span style=\" text-decoration: underline;\">Try the Trans button</span>. it opens a transparent always on top window you can drag over top of whatever your working on.</p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Step 3. When your ready to start some new projects click the plus button in the folders and tasks section to create new folders and tasks. You can right click folders and tasks to change colour, duplicate, rename etc. Ohhhh, and your mom says hi dude.</p></body></html>"
